      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> chopped parsley </strong>(save a little for garnish)<strong> </strong>and<strong> capers</strong> with your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, <strong>Dijon mustard </strong>and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and mix thoroughly – this is your <strong>salsa verde</strong></p>",
